{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**Root cause:** The DSL parser stores config values like `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` with the `file(...)` wrapper intact. The `handleAPIStepContent` handler was using this raw value directly as a file path (e.g., trying to read a file literally named `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`), which always failed.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:10:12.415036915Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:10:12.415054909Z"}
